{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Biscuit","content":["Preheat oven to 170°C and line two baking trays with baking paper.","Place butter, sugar and golden syrup in mixing bowl then cream <nobr>30 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","Add flour, cocoa powder, cornflour, water and salt then mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix again <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>, adding more water if dough does not start to clump together.","Tip out onto work surface and bring together into a ball. Between two pieces of cling film, roll dough out until 4-5 mm thick. Cut out rectangles (approx. 6 cm x 3 cm) using a sharp knife or pastry cutter, then use a palette knife to transfer biscuits to prepared baking trays, placing at least 2 cm apart.","Use a skewer to make shallow holes along the top of each biscuit (2 rows of 5 is the traditional number). Bake for 10-12 minutes (170°C). Leave on trays for 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool and harden. Meanwhile, prepare filling."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Place butter, icing sugar, cocoa powder, vanilla extract and boiling water in mixing bowl and mix <nobr>20 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix again <nobr>20 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>.","When biscuits are cool, spread some filling onto the underside of a biscuit and gently press another biscuit on top. Repeat until all biscuits are sandwiched together. Serve or store in an airtight container."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Biscuit","content":["110 g unsalted butter, diced","110 g light brown sugar","30 g golden syrup","170 g self-raising flour","60 g cocoa powder","60 g cornflour","30 - 45 g water","1 pinch fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["75 g unsalted butter, soft","150 g icing sugar","30 g cocoa powder","½ tsp vanilla extract","3 tsp water, boiling"]}],"id":"r97051","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-2uauX92YcjY\/XZau9wlT-DI\/AAAAAAAAhpU\/C7Os3tEgwrwFMbAxW69nG5eK2siNMu79wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_OL88vYUmYCDGs7a3.png","title":"Chocolate Bourbons","publishedAt":"2015-10-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"1.4 g","fat":"7 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"19.8 g","calories":"616 kJ \/ 147 kcal"},"usefulItems":"2 baking trays and baking paper, palette knife, long sharp knife, rolling pin, cling film, wire rack, skewer, airtight container, oven","basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","25 pieces"]}